    I like this product. It smells amazing. It is very low priced and does work well. However, I need to use quite a bit more product than I am used to for it to work as well as more expensive brands. I have fine hair (but lots of it!) down to my waist. I usually only use a half dollar size dollop of conditioner. I have to use a handful or more to get the same effect with this conditioner.
